- Invoke certify_round after each collection run (daemon + one-shot)
- Rotate full-catalog refresh across stores each cycle (CATALOG_STORES_PER_CYCLE)
- Full catalog sweep every 6 cycles as safety net
- Ship index_gate in collector Docker image for post-collect enrichment
- Pin cli-market-core @ 90fefe1 (1.10.0 + stores_fresh_24h stats)
